name: Plantuml-js
body:
### PlantUML-JS
A simple pegjs parser for PlantUML. 

Just that, no more, no less.

### Authors and Contributors
I'm @matthew-n and when I'm not doing this I'm Database Admin. So, please be kind with your criticisms and pull requests are very welcome.

### Support or Contact
Found a bug or a feature I missed go ahead and leave a [issue](https://github.com/matthew-n/plantuml-js/issues).
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
